	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, learn 6502 assembly, the NES's architecture, mappers and differences, mapper hacking, making a menu, etc.
<br />
<br />Or just put a bunch of NROM games inside the program files, although that still may require a little bit of 6502 assembly and programming.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
